      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 10:33:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场避险情绪高涨，拉美外汇表现落后于其他货币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/emerging-currencies-weaken-for-second-day-as-stocks-halt-selloff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于周三美国公布关键通胀数据之前全球市场避险情绪高涨，周二拉丁美洲货币表现不及新兴市场货币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/emerging-currencies-weaken-for-second-day-as-stocks-halt-selloff</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 09:36:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储会议前市场等待通胀数据 黄金价格波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/gold-steady-as-markets-await-inflation-data-ahead-of-fed-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员关注本周晚些时候公布的美国通胀数据，黄金价格出现波动，这可能为美联储的降息周期走向提供参考。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/gold-steady-as-markets-await-inflation-data-ahead-of-fed-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 23:37:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华尔街银行受创 股市涨势停滞：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员们为美国总统辩论和关键通胀数据做准备，大型银行股票遭到抛售，股市难以上涨。由于对需求受限的担忧，布伦特原油跌至 70 美元以下。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 22:27:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
